It’s not too late to join our growing family! Become a seed of legacy and together, let’s bloom beyond boundaries! 🌸✨

Sali na kayo please, sayang tumbling ng PRO namin. 😢

#KaPeacetahanNgAni 
#TamHunt2025
#ACP3PeaceTAYO

[UPDATE: PLEASE CHECK YOUR EMAILS! 🥹🤲]

LF: Omegaverse enjoyers 👀

Hi! We are fourth-year BA Communication students from FEU Manila, conducting our thesis entitled: “Are You Knotty or Nice?: Analyzing Sexual Fantasies and Consent-Making Among Queer Filipino Male Readers of Omegaverse Fiction”. 

If you:
• Identify as a queer man (incl. gay, bisexual, or other non-heterosexual identities),
• Are aged 18 or older
• Have read/engaged with AT LEAST 5 Omegaverse fanfiction (any fandom) published on Archive of Our Own (one of the five must feature male pregnancy)

Then you might be what we’re looking for 🤫 Let’s talk about heats, ruts, and A/B/O dynamics in depth, and contribute to conversations and research about the relationship of sex and media. 

Respondents are automatically granted 1 raffle entry.  
Refer a friend who signs up and names you as their referrer = 1 extra entry.
More details in the form.

Scan the QR code below or click the link to register:
https://forms.gle/xDcb99AbHKFAq4Qo6
https://forms.gle/xDcb99AbHKFAq4Qo6
https://forms.gle/xDcb99AbHKFAq4Qo6 

Should you have more questions, feel free to reach out via Messenger or via email: 2022021581@feu.edu.ph.
